Description: Scala-based Ethereum Classic client
 Fukuii is a fully-featured Ethereum Classic client written in Scala.
 It implements the Ethereum Classic protocol specification and provides
 support for mining, JSON-RPC API, and full node synchronization.
 .
 Features:
  * Full Ethereum Classic protocol support
  * JSON-RPC API for dApp development
  * Mining support
  * Configurable sync modes
  * Container-ready deployment
